The County Treasurer of Calvert County shall receive an annual salary of:
$46,875 for calendar year 2006;
$48,250 for calendar year 2007;
$49,625 for calendar year 2008; and
$51,000 for calendar year 2009 and each subsequent calendar year.

The County Treasurer of St. Mary's County shall receive an annual salary of:
$45,000 for the calendar year 2007;
$46,000 for the calendar year 2008;
$47,000 for the calendar year 2009; and
$48,000 for the calendar year 2010.

The County Treasurer of Garrett County shall receive:
$24,000 for calendar year 1991;
$26,000 for calendar year 1992;
$28,000 for calendar year 1993;
$30,000 for calendar year 1994; and
For each subsequent calendar year, the salary set by the County Commissioners in accordance with Chapter 91 of the Public Local Laws of Garrett County.

The annual salary of the County Treasurer of Kent County is:
$48,000 for the calendar year 2002;
$50,500 for the calendar year 2003;
$53,000 for the calendar year 2004;
$55,500 for the calendar year 2005; and
$58,000 for the calendar year 2006 and each subsequent calendar year.

The salary of the County Treasurer of Cecil County is:
$60,000 for calendar year 2006;
$66,250 for calendar year 2007;
$72,500 for calendar year 2008;
$78,750 for calendar year 2009; and
$85,000 for calendar year 2010 and each calendar year thereafter.
